            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the tagliatelle is cooking, add your <strong>chopped tomatoes</strong>, <strong>tomato paste</strong>, and <strong>vegetable stock mix </strong>to the pan with the chilli oil</p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong>, <strong>sugar</strong> and a grind of <strong>black pepper </strong>and cook for 2-3 min or until thickened</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
