            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once thickened, add the <strong>drained tagliatelle</strong> and<strong> broccoli </strong>to the pan, tear in <strong>half</strong> your <strong>basil </strong>(save the rest for garnish!) and give everything a gentle mix up until the pasta is coated in the sauce – this is your<strong> spicy arrabbiata sauce with fresh tagliatelle</strong></p><p>Tip: Add a splash of starchy pasta water if your sauce is looking a little dry</p>",
      "order": 7,
